description:
QosProfiles: Table storing QoS profile information for each cell, including timestamp, area, cell ID, and profile ID.
dateTime: Timestamp of QoS profile data record.
Area_Name: Name of the geographic area where the cell is located.
CellId: Unique identifier of the cell site.
Id2: Redundant cell identifier (appears to be a duplicate of CellId).
Id3:  Ancillary identifier (purpose unclear from sample data).
vsDataType: Type of data (always 'vsDataQosProfiles').
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format (always 'EricssonSpecificAttributes').
QosProfiles.qosProfilesId: Unique identifier for the QoS profile.
queries: Show me all QoS profiles for CellId 12345 in the Downtown area.
What's the QosProfiles.qosProfilesId for the profile active at CellId 67890 on 2024-10-27 10:00:00?
Retrieve all entries from QosProfiles where Area_Name = 'Uptown' and dateTime is between '2024-10-26 00:00:00' and '2024-10-27 00:00:00'.
List distinct QosProfiles.qosProfilesId values used in the 'Suburban' area.
How many unique CellIds are associated with qosProfilesId 'ProfileA' ?
